name: Team
sql:
CREATE TABLE "Team" (
"id" TEXT,
  "full_name" TEXT,
  "abbreviation" TEXT,
  "nickname" TEXT,
  "city" TEXT,
  "state" TEXT,
  "year_founded" INTEGER
)

name: Div_Conf

(

name: Win_Counts
sql:

)

)

name: dog
sql:
CREATE TABLE dog (
	"Id" INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	name VARCHAR(255), 
	color VARCHAR(255), 
	age INTEGER, 
	PRIMARY KEY ("Id")
)
